    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc"><ph props="android">Gets the <xref keyref="IMediaRecorder"/> object. </ph><ph props="ios mac">Creates an <xref keyref="IMediaRecorder"/> instance.</ph></ph></shortdesc>
